msgstr "Stock <em>Block Non-VPN Traffic</em> maps to <code>glvpn.general.block_non_vpn</code> when <code>/etc/config/glvpn</code> exists. <strong>Leave</strong> does not change vendor UCI. Prefer one strategy: this watchdog <em>or</em> vendor rules. v4.8+ may use the VPN Dashboard instead."

